p.k: A misplaced wallet and a considerate stranger are the elements that set "Lost and Found" in motion. Naomi is strolling along the beach and finds a wallet. The wallet's owner, Karol, is delighted by this act of kindness and invites her inside for a glass of water. As they laugh and chat attraction begins to develop and Karol, acting on impulse, plants a kiss on Naomi's lips... Romantic porn from Sex Art.
